<section>
  <title>Access to Released Versions of Draco</title>

  <para>The collection of Draco Libraries, header files, applications, unit
  tests, and documentation is periodically installed on various machines at
  LANL. These <emphasis role="bold">released</emphasis> versions of Draco can
  be found at the following locations:</para>

  <informaltable>
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <thead>
        <row>
          <entry align="center">Machines</entry>

          <entry align="center">Install Locations</entry>
        </row>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry>CCS-4 Linux LAN</entry>

          <entry><markup>/codes/radtran/vendors/draco/</markup></entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>ICNN (Theta, QSC, or Lambda)</entry>

          <entry><markup>/usr/projects/draco/</markup></entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

